query:
UPDATE EnvironmentMetrics
SET
  node_id = $2,
  time = $3,
  tempurature = $4,
  relative_humidity = $5,
  barometric_pressure = $6,
  gas_resistance = $7,
  iaq = $8,
  wind_direction = $9,
  wind_speed = $10,
  wind_gust = $11,
  wind_lull = $12,
  rainfall_1h = $13,
  rainfall_24h = $14,
  sensor_type = $15
WHERE
  msg_id = $1
